Achievements.Name: Frankenstein
Achievements.Description: Create a player in the Footy Factory.

Achievements.Name: The Ol' Switcheroo
Achievements.Description: Win a match using manual player-switching.

Achievements.Name: Tech Head
Achievements.Description: Win a video-referee decision in a Ranked Online match.

Achievements.Name: Winners
Achievements.Description: Win a match.

Achievements.Name: Skin of Your Teeth
Achievements.Description: Win a match in extra time.

Achievements.Name: On a String
Achievements.Description: Score a try from a grubber.

Achievements.Name: Unstoppable
Achievements.Description: Score 10 tries in a match.

Achievements.Name: Slow But Steady
Achievements.Description: Score a field goal from 30 metres out from the try line.

Achievements.Name: Sharp Shooter
Achievements.Description: Have a 100% conversion rate from 5 conversion attempts in a match.

Achievements.Name: Line Ball
Achievements.Description: Convert a try from the sideline.

Achievements.Name: Miserly
Achievements.Description: Force the opposition to play 65% or more in their defensive half.

Achievements.Name: Forward Thinking
Achievements.Description: Convert a try with a Forward.

Achievements.Name: Mind Reader
Achievements.Description: Intercept 3 passes in a match.

Achievements.Name: Hot Potato
Achievements.Description: Complete 7 passes or more in a single tackle phase.

Achievements.Name: 40/20 Vision
Achievements.Description: Kick a 40/20.

Achievements.Name: Touchy
Achievements.Description: Tackle the ball carrier into touch.

Achievements.Name: Drop Out
Achievements.Description: Tackle the ball carrier in their defensive try area.

Achievements.Name: Hero of the Moment
Achievements.Description: Perform a try-saving tackle close to the try line.

Achievements.Name: Pass the Parcel
Achievements.Description: Perform 10 offloads to receivers in a match.

Achievements.Name: Slippery
Achievements.Description: Successfully evade 3 tackles in a row on Veteran difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Coach Pleaser
Achievements.Description: Get a completion rate of 80% or more in a match.

Achievements.Name: World Beaters
Achievements.Description: Win the World Club Challenge in Career mode.

Achievements.Name: Profitable
Achievements.Description: Turn a profit every year in Career mode.

Achievements.Name: Simply The Best
Achievements.Description: Win an NRL or Super League Premiership.

Achievements.Name: Donuts

Achievements.Name: A Thumping
Achievements.Description: Win a match by more than 25 points on Legend difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Streaky
Achievements.Description: Win 3 consecutive matches with 1 team in an NRL or Super League Season.

Achievements.Name: Cool as a Cucumber
Achievements.Description: Kick a field goal to take the lead with 5 minutes left on the clock.

Achievements.Name: Marathon Man
Achievements.Description: Score a 85+ metre try on Legend difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Trick Shot
Achievements.Description: Successfully kick a conversion/goal kick while hitting the post.

Achievements.Name: Hat Trick
Achievements.Description: Score a hat trick of tries with one player.

Achievements.Name: Back-to-Back
Achievements.Description: Score a try in the first set of tackles after another try has been scored.

Achievements.Name: Superman
Achievements.Description: Win the Dally M or Man of Steel award in an NRL or Super League season in Career mode.

Achievements.Name: Golden Handshake
Achievements.Description: Complete a 10 year career.

Achievements.Name: Flawless Victory
Achievements.Description: With 1 team go through an NRL or Super League season without conceding a loss.
